posting_body: ['North Queen Anne Gem!', 'Property Address', '17 Etruria St Unit 201 | Seattle, WA 98109', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Lakeshore Corporation', 'Description', "Don't miss out on the opportunity to live in this charming North Queen Anne neighborhood!", 'Not only centrally located this unit also has a reserved parking space, balcony, fireplace, and secured entry.', 'Close to the bus line and just minutes from downtown!', "They say that location is everything, and at this property, you'll be near Amazon, SPU, Seattle Center, EMP, and everything that the Queen Area has to offer!!", 'Monthly Rent: $1,795 + $75 flat monthly fee for W/S/G + $25 per each additional occupant', 'Deposit: $1,000', 'Lease Term: 12-months', 'Pets are accepted on a case-by-case basis with additional fee(s) and/or pet rent.', 'Tenant pays electric.', '*$49 non-refundable application fee per each applicant age 18 and older.', 'Amenities', 'Great Location', 'Reserved Parking Space', 'Coin-operated Laundry On-site', 'Balcony', 'Fireplace', 'Close to Amazon', 'Close to Restaurants', 'Close to Shopping', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $49.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
